{"tid":1867644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[廣州封城]廣州所有居住小區實施封閉式管理","createTime":"2020-02-07T09:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T10:04:16.000Z","uid":50740,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e541146aa3b5dbd077336c6687fd8d9202383de0","tid":1867644,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:07:44.000Z","msg":"廣州市防控疫情工作指揮部發出通告，廣州所有居住小區實施封閉式管理，除速遞員和外賣員之外，非小區居民或車輛不得進入。速遞、外賣物品送到指定區域，由客戶自行領取；居民憑證出入，並要量體溫。<br />\n<br />\n通告又說，外地人及廣州居民由外地返回廣州，抵埗當天要通過微信程式申報或向所在單位及居委報告；對隱瞞去過重點疫區和健康狀況而造成疫情傳播的人，將追究責任；至於仍滯留重點疫區的人，在廣東省重大突發公共衛生事件一級響應解除前，不得返回廣州；最近14天從重點疫區抵達廣州的人，必須接受嚴格居家或集中隔離，一律不得外出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507236-20200207.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507236-20200207.htm&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=a6f505c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507236-20200207.htm&h=cabfb59d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507236-20200207.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1603ab4ae848f5456bd7d8b5c1f04b5da5d820ef","tid":1867644,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:10:07.000Z","msg":"大獲,咁近"},{"pid":"b75bfe001219a94371a7c121f4f529e611820ff3","tid":1867644,"uid":293677,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n7MNJyb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn7MNJyb.jpg&h=055644d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a4deaa75293e05e7f9b9979311d27da8972bd05","tid":1867644,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:19:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3924764a11bf02e81449e453a4e99124e7bc89de","tid":1867644,"uid":168730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:27:00.000Z","msg":"利害了 你的國"},{"pid":"f7845f2b27becf7909